race.comment: ANJO ZEPHYR (6) boasts a strong record this journey with three wins and two minors from six tries. Scored by 9 lengths last time (17.89) in a Grade 5 over 320m at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. WICKED RAVEN (1) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (18.48) at this track. Leading chance. CHRIS WHIT (2) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her swift win the start prior, getting around this track over 320m in 18.28. Expecting another bold showing. RED ROCK RATTLER (8) is in form and worth thought again.
